kubestate-metrics
It is a service inside kubernetes cluster used to get the information about the cluster objects like pods,deployment.

deployed a kubestate-metrics using the helm 
cmd - helm install kube-state-metrics prometheus-community/kube-state-metrics --namespace monitoring

aftet the instalation of the metrics we can check with the command

kubectl get pods -n monitoring

kubernetes % kubectl get secret --namespace monitoring prometheus-grafana -o jsonpath="{.data.admin-password}" | base64 --decode - the command used to get password of a grafana dashboard.

username - admin
password - from the previous command

